Nmap is far more than a port scanner—it is a powerful reconnaissance framework capable of performing **deep HTTP enumeration and WAF detection**.

By leveraging NSE scripts, security professionals can:

* Identify web technologies
* Detect defensive mechanisms
* Improve both offensive and defensive strategies

